<html><body bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><div>May I suggest a Worl &amp; PDF version option. I built a reporting engine for Wells Fargo and it was always good practice to provide a comprehensive report and allow managers the flexibility to remove fields that were irrelevant and/or add notes to the report before distributing it.<br><br>Kaushal</div><div><br>On Feb 11, 2010, at 10:55 AM, Henry Addo &lt;<a href="mailto:henry@...">henry@...</a>&gt; wrote:<br><br></div><div></div><blockquote type="cite"><div>Good idea in fact. The report is really detailed. If we could provide other versions too, I think people will be interested. Say much trimmed version of the whole report. I'm sure people will be interested in getting specific reports.&nbsp;<div>

